p: In Inferior Court of King County, Washington Ty. No 5662 Order
In Re Application of Alice McKay for Writ of Habeas Corpus to obtain possession of Mary McKay

Now May 5, 1891 on presentation and reading of affidavit of Della Keevan a warrant is directed to issue for the arrest of Alice McKay and Katie McKay Dre formely Katie McKay whose marriage name is unkonwn for contempt without bail, as prayed for in said affidavit.
